# 🚀 Day 71/90 – Connect the App to the OCR Service

Welcome to **Day 71!**

Yesterday we created the `OCRService`.

Today we'll make the app actually **use** that service.

Right now:

```text
Report Screen
      ↓
sample_report.dart
```

After today:

```text
Report Screen
      ↓
OCR Service
      ↓
